Tutab is a monkey merchant who sells magical items on Ape Atoll at his stall, Tutab's Magical Market. It can only be used after completion of Monkey Madness I, and whilst wielding a greegree and Monkeyspeak amulet.

His shop is the only way to obtain another monkey talisman, other than talking to the Monkey Child. At 65 Thieving and whilst in human form, players can steal from his magic stall, granting 100 Thieving experience and one of the four elemental runes (air, fire, water, earth) or a law rune. It takes about 40 seconds before it can be pilfered again.
